<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <BaseHead title="Maths Resources" description="Discover our curated collection of resources for Maths to help you learn and revise effectively." />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    </head>
    <body>
        <Header />
        <main>
            <div class="resource-intro-container">
                <h1>Mathematics Resources</h1>
                <p>
                    Mathematics is all about practice and understanding the core concepts. Our hand-picked resources are designed to help you tackle everything from foundational algebra to complex calculus. Dive in and find guides, videos, and tips to help you excel in your exams.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="resources-container">
                <section class="resource-section">
                    <h2 class="resource-heading">TedEd Maths Videos</h2>
                    <ul class="resource-list">
                        <li>
                            <strong>Five Principles of Extraordinary Math Teaching - Dan Finkel</strong>
                            <p>These are some amazing ideas which we try to stick to as much as possible in our teaching.</p>
                            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ytVneQUA5-c" class="resource-link">Watch Now →</a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>4 Steps to Unlock Your Kid's Math Potential - Shalinee Sharma</strong>
                            <p>A way you as a parent can help your child with maths.</p>
                            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hg_xzFJ4ZAA" class="resource-link">Watch Now →</a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Why do people get so anxious about math? - Orly Rubinsten</strong>
                            <p>A delve into understanding the anxiety some students face around maths.</p>
                            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7snnRaC4t5c" class="resource-link">Watch Now →</a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>What Makes People Engage With Math - Grant Sanderson</strong>
                            <p>How to make maths engaging and breakthrough to kids who can't connect with the subject.</p>
                            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s_L-fp8gDzY" class="resource-link">Watch Now →</a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Our Favourite Maths Youtube Channel - Numberphile</strong>
                            <p>Full of interesting maths ideas which can show the beauty and wonder in maths.</p>
                            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@numberphile" class="resource-link">Explore the Channel →</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </section>
                <section class="resource-section">
                    <h2 class="resource-heading">Interesting Maths Channels</h2>
                    <ul class="resource-list">
                        <li>
                            <strong>3Blue1Brown</strong>
                            <p>A great channel full of engaging topics to change how your child thinks about maths.</p>
                            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@3blue1brown" class="resource-link">Watch Now →</a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Numberphile</strong>
                            <p>Full of interesting maths ideas which can show the beauty and wonder in maths.</p>
                            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@numberphile" class="resource-link">Explore the Channel →</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </section>
                
                
            </div>

            <div class="cta-section">
                <h2>Need Personalized Maths Help?</h2>
                <p>Our expert maths tutors are ready to help you with your specific challenges. Book a free consultation today to create a customized learning plan.</p>
                <a href="/consultations" class="cta-button">
                    Book Your Free Consultation
                </a>
            </div>
        </main>
        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>

<style>
    main {
        color: var(--accent);
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 2em auto;
        padding: 0 1em;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .resource-intro-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 3em;
    }

    .resource-intro-container h1 {
        font-size: clamp(1.8em, 5vw, 2.5em);
        margin-bottom: 0.5em;
    }

    .resource-intro-container p {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        font-size: clamp(1em, 2vw, 1.1em);
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .resources-container {
        display: grid;
        gap: 2.5em;
        padding: 0 1em;
    }

    .resource-section {
        border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gray-light);
        padding-bottom: 2em;
    }

    .resource-section:last-of-type {
        border-bottom: none;
    }
    
    .resource-heading {
        font-size: clamp(1.5em, 4vw, 1.8em);
        color: var(--accent);
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 1em;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .resource-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        display: grid;
        gap: 1.5em;
    }

    .resource-list li {
        background-color: var(--card-bg-color);
        padding: 1.5em;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
        background-color: white;
    }

    .resource-list li strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: clamp(1.1em, 2.5vw, 1.25em);
        color: var(--accent);
        margin-bottom: 0.5em;
    }

    .resource-list li p {
        margin: 0 0 1em;
        font-size: clamp(1em, 2vw, 1.1em);
    }

    .resource-link {
        color: var(--accent-pop);
        font-weight: bold;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .resource-link:hover {
        color: var(--accent-dark);
        text-decoration: underline;
    }
    
    /* Final CTA Section */
    .cta-section {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 4em;
        padding: 2.5em;
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
        color: var(--accent);
    }
    
    .cta-section h2 {
        font-size: clamp(1.5em, 4vw, 1.8em);
        margin-top: 0;
        color: var(--accent);
    }
    .cta-section p {
        margin-bottom: 1.5em;
    }

    .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 1em 2em;
        background-color: var(--accent-pop);
        color: white;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .resources-container {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(1, 1fr);
        }
    }
</style>